high_descs: Go forward. Passing the furniture on the left, turn left. Go forward until you reach the countertop. Turn left and move on. Then turn right and get near the microwave.
Turn left. Go to the sink and turn right.
Place the soup bowl in the sink. Turn on the faucet for 6 seconds. Turn the faucet off. Take the soup bowl.
Turn right. Reach the microwave, turn left.
Open the microwave. Place the bowl at the back of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Find a soup bowl. Wet it. Place it inside a microwave oven.

high_descs: Turn around from the hall and head towards the countertop.
Pick the bowl from the kitchen slab.
Take the bowl towards the kitchen sink.
Wash the bowl in the kitchen and pick it from it.
Take the washed bowl towards the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the bowl inside of it.
anns.task_desc: Pick the bowl from the kitchen, wash , and place inside of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and head straight to the countertop.
Pick the bowl from the countertop.
Turn left and move to the sink on your right.
Put the bowl in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn right and head to the microwave on your left.
Place the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl in the microwave.
